!Discipline Focus (Ex)

At 1st level, a monk gain the benefits of the Weapon Focus feat with weapons associated with a martial discipline of her choice, chosen from the list of the six monk disciplines (Desert Wind, Diamond Mind, Setting Sun, Shadow Hand, Stone Dragon, and Tiger Claw).